snippet.title: Amber Lawrence - Things That Bring Me Down [Official Video]
snippet.description:
Things That Bring Me Down is the 2nd song from Amber's 2007 album, The Mile.

www.amberlawrence.com.au

----

Lyrics:
I cry too much coz i love to eat
I drank cheap wine it smelled so sweet
And I'm way too tired, coz i stayed all night with you
The rooms a mess but it's all my things
This gorgeous dress, I worked the week so my rent ain't cheap
Coz i'm paying for the veiw
Oh, the things that bring me down, feel good

And I know I'm gonna feel like hell tomorrow
Just one last kiss
And I know that I could end up sad and sorry
It's worth the risk
Cos it feels like heaven at 3am
When I don't do what I should
Oh, the things that bring me down, feel good

Drove all night to the doughnut store
We ate too much
The loft weigh more
We may work late
The boss never understood
Oh, the things that bring me down, feel good

And I know I'm gonna feel like hell tomorrow
Just one last kiss
And I know that I could end up sad and sorry
It's worth the risk
Cos it feels like heaven at 3am
When I don't do what I should
Oh, the things that bring me down, feel good

And I know I'm gonna feel like hell tomorrow
Just one last kiss
And I know that I could end up sad and sorry
It's worth the risk
Cos it feels like heaven at 3am
When I don't do what I should
Oh, the things that bring me down

-----

Written by:
Amber Lawrence
